## Day 1 — Intro to AI APIs (like OpenAI), Prompt Engineering Basics

🟢 **Beginner:** An **AI API** lets your app send text to a powerful language model and get an intelligent reply — like having ChatGPT inside Zero Hunger. **Prompt engineering** is the skill of phrasing your instructions so the model returns exactly what you want.

🔵 **Advanced:** You send a request (model name + messages/input) and receive generated text, billed per **token**. Craft prompts with a clear **system role** (the AI's persona and rules), few-shot **examples**, and explicit output format — for structured needs, ask for **JSON** and parse it. Control behavior with parameters like `temperature` (creativity vs determinism). Watch for **latency, cost, rate limits, and hallucination**; never trust output blindly for critical logic. Keep the API key server-side and proxy requests through your Express backend.

